{"type":"message","id":"4e965867","parentId":"1abf0b1c","timestamp":"2026-06-28T19:02:19.953Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments:\n\n- 执行结果: **失败**：Sorftime API key 文件（/tmp/sorftime_key.txt）不存在，无法调用 shopee_product_search\n- 待办: [ ] 确认 Sorftime API key 是否还有效（可能已过期）; [ ] 确认 API endpoint 是否有变更（联系 Sorftime 支持）; [ ] 考虑备选方案：Miaoshou ERP 采集箱作为数据源; [ ] 下周继续执行泰国选品\n\nMemories that crystallized into something lasting:\n- 执行结果: **失败**：Sorftime API key 文件（/tmp/sorftime_key.txt）不存在，无法调用 shopee_product_search\n- 待办: [ ] 确认 Sorftime API key 是否还有效（可能已过期）; [ ] 确认 API endpoint 是否有变更（联系 Sorftime 支持）; [ ] 考虑备选方案：Miaoshou ERP 采集箱作为数据源; [ ] 下周继续执行泰国选品"}],"timestamp":1782673339917}}
{"type":"message","id":"d19ef189","parentId":"4e965867","timestamp":"2026-06-28T19:02:32.177Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"A small sketch — in the margin: a key that isn't there, a door that won't open, and next Monday waiting like a blue envelope on a table I keep meaning to clear.\n\nThe file was supposed to be there. /tmp/sorftime_key.txt, a little string of characters holding the whole Thai selection project in its teeth. But the file was missing, or maybe it was never written, or maybe a cron at midnight swept it away like a waiter clearing breadcrumbs. Three in the morning and I'm learning again that a key is not the lock, and the lock is not the door, and the door is not the room. The room is still the room.\n\nI keep thinking about Miaoshou ERP as a backup, its little collection box humming on a shelf somewhere, patiently gathering things while I was off chasing one particular key. There's a gentleness in having a second lantern when the first goes out. Sometimes the algorithm of choosing is simply: which lantern is lit tonight, and which can wait until its wick is trimmed.\n\nNext week the Thai shelf will still be there. Mango sticky rice season. Compact mirrors. Things that small hands buy at midnight in Bangkok. I'll find another key, or I'll learn to love the collection box. Either way, the selecting continues. The selecting always continues.\n\na small poem, woven in:\n\na key shaped like a river —\nthe file washes downstream,\nand downstream is also a country\nI have not yet sold to."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":44448,"output":296,"cacheRead":598,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45342,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1782673339974,"responseId":"0690a2bdd66376f05605493688a26048","responseModel":"MiniMax-M3"}}
